Avoidance, in total, is capped to 75%. This is a value that is a combined

value of parry, block, and dodge in that order of precedence. If you have 50%

parry and 25% block, you are capped at 75% avoidance. If you have 50% block,

25% block, and 25% dodge, you only get the first 75%, and do not get any dodge


 Note that for every 2 levels above the victim, each avoidance is reduced by

1%.

